item.title: About me
item.description: ❗Page Under Construction 🚧 🤠 whoami Recently, my work and personal interest has been in the area of computer vision and its applications in robotics. As a component of my Master’s degree I completed an individual study module with the Robotics and Perception research group at UZH. This study involved gaining familiarity with Event-Based Vision and its application in solving problems such as VIO, SLAM and it’s potential in various reconstruction algorithms.
